perv
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(also pervo) a person who watches another or others with erotic or sexual interest (AOD/NZOD distinguishes from a sexual pervert as such - valid?); the act of so watching; an illicit or lustful look; (more neutrally) a look (around)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also perve
